t data protection rules than in your country. The Company will implement commercially reasonable and appropriate safeguards to protect your information in accordance with our Privacy Policy. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and you agree that the Company is not liable for any unauthorized access or disclosure outside of our reasonable control.</p>\n<p><strong>Service Availability and Changes</strong><br />The Company does not guarantee that the Application, or any content or features within it, will always be available, uninterrupted, or error free. The Company reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the Application, or any part thereof, at any time without notice or liability. Personalized experiences, including those powered by artificial intelligence, may change over time and are not guaranteed to produce specific results.</p>\n<p><strong>Prohibited Conduct</strong><br />In addition to the restrictions set forth elsewhere in this Agreement, you agree not to:<br />(a) use the Application for any purpose that is illegal, unlawful, or prohibited by this Agreement;<br />(b) engage in fraudulent, deceptive, or manipulative behavior, including attempting to game or exploit the Application&rsquo;s rewards or personalization systems;<br />(c) harass, threaten, or otherwise harm other users; or<br />(d) interfere with or disrupt the operation of the Application, servers, or networks connected to the Application.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"custom_section_enabled":true,"custom_section_title":{"en":"Additional Acknowledgements"},"customizations":{"accordionStyle":"disabled","advancedSeoControl":true,"borderStyle":"shadow","cssText":"","hide_poweredby":true,"lastUpdated":"2025-09-07T08:16:17.707707-04:00","removeTitles":false,"title":"{\"en\":\"End User License Agreement (EULA)\",\"fr\":\"Coup de couche\",\"es\":\"Eula\",\"pt-BR\":\"Eula\",\"pt-PT\":\"Eula\",\"it\":\"Eula\",\"de\":\"Eula\",\"nl\":\"Eula\",\"bg\":\"EULA\",\"cs\":\"EU